  "description": "Annual herb from Asteraceae, domesticated from Mediterranean wild ancestor *L. serriola*. Produces rosette of leaves varying from loose and dissected to tightly heading, with variable latex content in petioles and phloem. Bolts rapidly under long daylength and heat stress; seed germination inhibited above 25°C (thermoinhibition).",
